Hello, I will be teaching you how to use your local PHPMYADMIN to connect to this remote database
1. Go to your XAMPP directory
2. Access C:\xampp\phpMyAdmin\config.inc.php
3. Add this to the end of the file

$i++;
$cfg['Servers'][$i]['host'] = 'sql12.freesqldatabase.com:3306'; //provide hostname and port if other than default
$cfg['Servers'][$i]['user'] = 'sql12178500'; 	//user name for your remote server
$cfg['Servers'][$i]['password'] = 'u5e8Bt8RGa';  //password
$cfg['Servers'][$i]['auth_type'] = 'config';
Break





